@startuml
title Proxy remoto - servicio externo
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  interface CurrencyService <<Subject>> {
+convertUsdToClp(usd: double): double
  }
  class RemoteCurrencyService <<RealSubject>>
  class CurrencyRemoteProxy <<Proxy>>
}

CurrencyService <|.. RemoteCurrencyService
CurrencyService <|.. CurrencyRemoteProxy
CurrencyRemoteProxy --> RemoteCurrencyService : controla/delega
Main ..> CurrencyService : usa misma interfaz

note bottom of CurrencyRemoteProxy
Representa localmente un objeto remoto y oculta los detalles de comunicacion.
end note
@enduml
